title: Christina King - Pure Freedom (Chastity) [audio presentation]
description:
Christina King - Pure Freedom (Chastity) [audio presentation]

In this very unique presentation, Christina King, mother of seven, shares in a powerful way the beauty of the Sacraments and how through them the virtue of chastity and the discipline of abstinence can save not only the body, but especially the soul.
